et%20held%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Rajkhowa-faction%20after%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20agreement%20in%20Delhi%20said%2097%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20126%20assembly%20seats%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98reserved%E2%80%99%20for%20indigenous%20people%20but%20the%20parameters%20of%20declaring%20who%20is%20indigenous%20would%20be%20in%20accordance%20to%20the%20broad%20guidelines%20and%20methodology%20adopted%20for%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20state%20in%202023.%20The%20ULFA%20leaders%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20MHA%20has%20told%20them%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20consider%E2%80%9D%20recommending%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20guidelines%20for%20future%20delimitation%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investment%20of%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20crore%2C%20staggered%20through%20years%2C%20is%20also%20a%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20promise%20under%20the%20agreement%2C%20besides%20declaring%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20annual%20floods%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98national%20priority%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20agreement%2C%20the%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20soon%20to%20look%20into%20reservations%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20at%20the%20panchayat%20level%3B%20also%20relook%20at%20the%20updated%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRCs)%20and%20make%20voter%20enumeration%20process%20stricter%3B%20and%20land%20evicted%20by%20encroachers%20would%20to%20be%20distributed%20among%20landless%20indigenous%20people.%20A%20committee%20would%20look%20into%20the%20issue%20of%20sick%20tea%20gardens%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outfit%E2%80%99s%20founding%20leaders%20including%20Anup%20Chetia%20and%20Sasadhar%20Choudhury%20present%20at%20the%20press%20meet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fassam%2Fcentre-assam-government-sign-peace-accord-with-pro-talks-faction-of-ulfa-2829198%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20would%20disband%20the%20outfit%3B%20their%20cadres%20would%20vacate%20the%20designated%20camps%20being%20run%20by%20the%20government%20since%202008%3B%20their%20arms%20kept%20in%20joint%20custody%20with%20the%20government%20since%20would%20be%20surrendered%20to%20the%20authorities%20too.%20They%20also%20said%20they%20have%20no%20political%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20they%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20agreed%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20state%20till%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20is%20hearing%20a%20set%20of%20petitions%20on%20it%2C%20gives%20its%20final%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20both%20Shah%20and%20Sarma%20termed%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98golden%20day%E2%80%99%20for%20Assam.%20Shah%20gave%20all%20credit%20to%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cvision%20for%20a%20prosperous%2C%20peaceful%20and%20developed%20Northeast%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20turn%2C%20Modi%2C%20on%20X%2C%20said%20the%20agreement%20%E2%80%9Cmarked%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20peace%20and%20development%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20peace%20and%20development.%20This%20agreement%2C%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20lasting%20progress%20in%20Assam.%20I%20commend%20the%20efforts%20of%20all%20involved%20in%20this%20landmark%20achievement.%20Together%2C%20we%20move%20towards%20a%20future%20of%20unity%2C%20growth%2C%20and%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FY8sqPr1KPJ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FY8sqPr1KPJ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%4