s%20a%20peace%20agreement%20or%20an%20%E2%80%9Celection%20manifesto%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20not%20fulfilled%20any%20of%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Assamese%20people.%20Land%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20rights%2C%20culture%2C%20language%20and%20identity%20%E2%80%93%20nothing%20of%20these%20have%20been%20protected%20through%20the%20pact%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gogoi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20cadres%20have%20been%20in%20designated%20camps%20since%202008%2C%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20the%20ULFA%20signed%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20only%20in%202011%2C%20and%20has%20since%20been%20in%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Centre%20for%20a%20peace%20deal.%20Several%20times%2C%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20interlocutors%20have%20been%20changed%3B%20twice%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20break%20in%20the%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20UPA%20era%2C%20though%20the%20Rajkhowa%20group%20had%20shunned%20the%20demand%20to%20the%20Centre%20to%20discuss%20the%20sovereignty%E2%80%99%20issue%20of%20Assam%2C%20the%20Paresh%20Barua%20faction%20of%20the%20outfit%20%E2%80%93%20ULFA-Independent%20%E2%80%93%20has%20not.%20The%20Barua%20faction%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20smaller%20in%20size%20than%20the%20Rajkhowa%E2%80%99s%20overground%20faction%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20camping%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESigning%20the%20agreement%2C%20Rajkhowa%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20contribution%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20former%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Tarun%20Gogoi%20for%20having%20started%20the%20peace%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703919572000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fulfa-faction-signs-peace-accord-with-centre-poli