od%2Fnews%2Furvashi-rautela-extends-a-heartfelt-welcome-to-animal-star-bobby-deol-in-the-nbk109-family%2Farticleshow%2F106395261.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106395261.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBobby%20Deol%20joins%20the%20cast%20of%20'NBK%20109%2C'%20directed%20by%20KS%20Ravindra%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Bobby%20Kolli.%20Urvashi%20Rautela%20expresses%20excitement%20about%20working%20with%20Deol%20and%20thanks%20the%20Deol%20family%20for%20launching%20her%20into%20the%20film%20industry.%20'NBK%20109'%20features%20a%20star-studded%20cast%20including%20Nandamuri%20Balakrishna%2C%20Dulquer%20Salmaan%2C%20Payal%20Rajput%2C%20Ronit%20Roy%2C%20Prakash%20Raj%2C%20Chandini%20Chowdary%2C%20and%20Krishna%20Murali%20Posani.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PCB%20To%20Knock%20ICC's%20Door%20Over%20Rizwan's%20'Wristband%20Dismissal'%20Controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20controversial%20dismissal%20of%20Mohammed%20Rizwan%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20Australia%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20umpiring%20and%20use%20of%20technology%20with%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC).%20On%20Friday%2C%20the%20on-field%20umpire%20refused%20to%20give%20Rizwan%20out%20after%20Australian%20captain%20and%20pacer%20Pat%20Cummins%20appealed%20for%20a%20caught%20behind%2C%20but%20the%20home%20side%20managed%20to%20overturn%20the%20decision%20through%20the%20DRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20camp%20was%20less%20than%20happy%20about%20the%20reversal%20of%20the%20decision%20after%20the%20%E2%80%98Snickometer'%20showed%20a%20spike%20on%20it%20when%20the%20ball%20was%20just%20above%20the%20wrist%20of%20Rizwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20reliable%20source%20within%20the%20PCB%20said%20its%20head%20Zaka%20Ashraf%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20team%20director%20Mohammed%20Hafeez%2C%20who%20conveyed%20some%20points%20to%20him%20about%20the%20umpiring%20and%20the%20use%20of%20technology%20during%20the%20Melbourne%20Test%20which%20they%20lost%20by%2079%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20PCB%20is%20all%20set%20to%20raise%20those%20points%20with%20the%20global%20governing%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20rules%20and%20regulations%20governing%20cricket%20and%20the%20use%20of%20technology%20on%20the%20field%20is%20approved%20by%20the%20ICC%20Executive%20Board%20after%20being%20vetted%20by%20the%20MCC%20Cricket%20Committee%20and%20ICC%20Cricket%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHafeez%20was%20visibly%20upset%20during%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%20at%20the%20MCG%20on%20Friday%2C%20while%20stressing%20on%20the%20need%20to%20highlight%20inconsistent%20umpiring%20and%20the%20challenges%20of%20technology%20which%20had%20influenced%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20entire%20game%2C%20there%20were%20very%20inconsistent%20decisions%20by%20the%20umpires.%20We%20play%20this%20beautiful%20game%20of%20cricket%20with%20natural%20instinct%2C%20and%20we%20all%20know%20the%20basics%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20at%20times%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20focus%20is%20more%20on%20technology%20than%20on%20the%20actual%20cricket%20being%20played.%20I%20believe%20this%20is%20an%20area%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20Hafeez%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20also%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20clarity%20and%20certainty%20in%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20against%20technology%20in%20the%20game.%20But%20if%20it%20brings%20doubt%20and%20confusion%2C%20it%20is%20not%20acceptable.%20Some%20decisions%20were%20not%20understandable.%20The%20ball%20hitting%20the%20stumps%20is%20always%20out.%20I%20will%20never%20understand%20why%20there%20is%20an%20umpire's%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20detailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHafeez%20said%20he%20had%20a%20talk%20with%20Rizwan%20and%20the%20wicketkeeper%20batter%20told%20him%20that%20the%20ball%20did%20not%20touch%20his%20gloves%2C%20and%20there%20should%20be%20conclusive%20evidence%20to%20overturn%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20on-field%20umpire.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703913000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffa85nc4g_mohammad-rizwan-afp_625x300_30_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-cricket-board-to-knock-iccs-door-over-mohammad-rizwans-wristband-dismissal-controversy-report-4767991%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Friday%2C%20the%20on-field%20umpire%20refused%20to%20give%20Rizwan%20out%20after%20Australian%20captain%20and%20pacer%20Pat%20Cummins%20appealed%20for%20a%20caught%20behind%2C%20but%20the%20home%20side%20managed%20to%20overturn%20the%20decision%20through%20the%20DRS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-cricket-board-to-knock-iccs-door-over-mohammad-rizwans-wristband-dismissal-controversy-report-4767991%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-cricket-board-to-knock-iccs-door-over-mohammad-rizwans-wristband-dismissal-controversy-report-4767991%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-cricket-board-to-knock-iccs-door-over-mohammad-rizwans-wristband-dismissal-controversy-report-4767991%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amritsar%20Delhi%20Vande%20Bharat%3A%20Golden%20Temple%20town%20to%20Delhi%20in%206hrs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703912553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106394897%2Cimgsize-66442.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fvande-bharat-express-amritsar-delhi-train-number-schedule-route-fare-stoppages-ticket-price-speed-start-date-new-route%2Farticleshow%2F106394834.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amritsar%20to%20Delhi%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%3A%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20on%20December%2030%2C%202023%20flag%20off%20the%20new%20Amritsar%20to%20Delhi%20Junction%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20train.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dua%20Lipa%2C%20Shakira%2C%20Viral%20Instagram%20posts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703912348000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106394817%2Cimgsize-55382.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fdua-lipa-shakira-kanye-west-celebs-instagram-posts-that-went-viral-this-week%2Farticleshow%2F106394478.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106394478.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20year%20came%20to%20a%20close%2C%20Hollywood%20stars%20were%20at%20their%20best%20behaviour.%20From%20Dua%20Lipa%20being%20spotted%20in%20India%20to%20Shakira%20being%20honoured%20with%20a%20statue%20and%20Kanye%20West%20apologising%20for%20his%20anti-Semitic%20comments%2C%20here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20photos%20that%20went%20viral%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hafeez%20Blames%20%26quot%3BInconsistent%20Umpiring%20And%20Technology%20Curse%26quot%3B%20For%20Pak's%20Loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20suffered%20a%2079-run%20loss%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20at%20Melbourne%20Cricket%20Ground%20on%20Friday.%20The%20result%20saw%20the%20guests%20also%20losing%20the%20series%20with%20a%20match%20to%20go.%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20director%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Hafeez%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F557-mohammad-hafeez-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Hafeez%3C%2Fa%3E%20believes%20that%20%26quot%3Binconsistent%20umpiring%20and%20technology%20curse%26quot%3B%20cost%20the%20side%20the%20match.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20Pakistan%20needed%2098%20runs%20with%205%20wickets%20in%20hand%20in%20the%20chase%20of%20317%20when%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20was%20caught%20behind.%20The%20ball%20hit%20the%20wristband%20of%20Rizwan's%20glove%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Alex%20Carey%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64136-alex-carey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAlex%20Carey%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20the%20catch%20behind%20the%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGround%20umpire%20Michael%20Gough%20was%20unconvinced%20with%20the%20appeal%20but%20Australia%20decided%20to%20go%20upstairs.%20During%20the%20DRS%20review%2C%20third%20umpire%20Richard%20Illingworth%20felt%20there%20was%20conclusive%20evidence%20through%20Hotspot%20and%20Real-Time%20Snicko%20to%20decide%20that%20the%20ball%20had%20brushed%20Rizwan's%20wristband.%20Hence%2C%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20ground%20umpire%20was%20overturned%20and%20Rizwan%20was%20adjudged%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncluding%20the%20dismissal%20of%20Rizwan%2C%20Pakistan%20lost%20their%20last%20five%20wickets%20for%2018%20runs%2C%20suffering%20a%20disappointing%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20made%20some%20mistakes%20as%20a%20team%2C%20we%20will%20take%20that%2C%20we%20will%20address%20those%20things%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20I%20believe%20inconsistent%20umpiring%20and%20technology%20curse%20(has)%20really%20given%20us%20the%20result%20which%20should%20have%20been%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hafeez%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20these%20are%20the%20areas%20that%20need%20to%20be%20addressed.%20I%20spoke%20to%20(Rizwan)%20and%20he's%20a%20very%20honest%20person.%20He%20said%20he%20did%20not%20even%20feel%20that%20it%20touched%20anywhere%20near%20the%20gloves.%20And%20what%20we%20saw%2C%20there%20should%20be%20conclusive%20evidence%20to%20reverse%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20umpire.%20That's%20what%20I%20know.%20The%20umpire%20gave%20it%20not%20out%20and%20there%20was%20no%20conclusive%20kind%20of%20evidence%20where%20the%20decision%20has%20to%20be%20turned%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%2C%20I'm%20in%20favor%20of%20that%2C%20but%20(only)%20if%20it's%20giving%20you%20benefit.%20But%20if%20it's%20bringing%20some%20doubts%20and%20bringing%20some%20curse%20into%20the%20game%2C%20it%20should%20not%20be%20accepted%20by%20anyone.%20I%20think%20technology%20is%20something%20that%20is%20taking%20away%20from%20the%20instinct%20of%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703911320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F68n3ptj_mohammad-rizwan-angry-afp_625x300_30_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammad-hafeez-blames-inconsistent-umpiring-and-technology-curse-for-pakistans-loss-to-australia-in-second-test-4764318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20suffered%20a%2079-run%20loss%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20at%20Melbourne%20Cricket%20Ground%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammad-hafeez-blames-inconsistent-umpiring-and-technology-curse-for-pakistans-loss-to-australia-in-second-test-4764318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammad-hafeez-blames-inconsistent-umpiring-and-technology-curse-for-pakistans-loss-to-australia-in-second-test-4764318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fmohammad-hafeez-blames-inconsistent-umpiring-and-technology-curse-for-pakistans-loss-to-australia-in-second-test-4764318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20JDU%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Existential%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%20again%20and%20will%20perform%20the%20double%20role%20of%20party%20president%20and%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister.%20Four%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20his%20predecessor%2C%20offered%20his%20resignation%20to%20focus%20on%20contesting%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20was%2C%20reports%20suggest%2C%20not%20very%20happy%20with%20Lallan%20Singh's%20growing%20proximity%20to%20rival-turned-friend%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20family.%20The%20move%20suggests%20Nitish%20Kumar%20wants%20control%20over%20the%20party%20organization%20as%20well%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20are%20questions%20about%20the%20future%20of%20JDU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELallan%20Singh%20joins%20the%20long%20list%20of%20leaders%20whom%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20sidelined%20over%20the%20years%2C%20including%20George%20Fernandes%2C%20Sharad%20Yadav%2C%20RCP%20Singh%2C%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%2C%20and%20Jiten%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20for%20his%20political%20gains.%20In%20Bihar's%20political%20circles%2C%20the%20popular%20saying%20goes%2C%20%26quot%3BAisa%20koi%20saga%20nahin%2C%20jise%20Nitish%20ne%20thaga%20nahin%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20is%20reportedly%20upset%20about%20being%20left%20out%20of%20the%20race%20for%20convenor%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20which%20his%20party%20claims%20he%20is%20the%20founding%20member.%20The%20poor%20showing%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20in%20recent%20polls%20may%20also%20have%20seeded%20doubts%20in%20his%20mind%20about%20INDIA's%20prospects%20in%202024.%20With%20opinion%20polls%20and%20analysts%20predicting%202024%20is%20a%20done%20deal%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20Nitish%20has%20bigger%20things%20to%20worry%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20is%20not%20a%20family-controlled%20regional%20party%2C%20unlike%20most%20others%20like%20RJD%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20YSRCP%2C%20TDP%2C%20BRS%2C%20DMK%2C%20SHS%2C%20and%20NCP%2C%20so%20no%20leader%20has%20wider%20acceptance%2C%20apart%20from%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20He%20hasn't%20declared%20a%20successor%20like%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20has%20in%20Odisha.%20So%20the%20future%20of%20JDU%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20a%20big%20question.%20What%20is%20his%20gameplan%20for%202024%20and%202025%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20mostly%20consists%20of%20leaders%20from%20the%20former%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20who%20left%20when%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20George%20Fernandes%20broke%20away%20over%20differences%20with%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20formed%20their%20own%20outfit%2C%20Samata%20Party%2C%20in%20the%201990s.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20leaders%20from%20the%20RJD%2C%20Congress%20and%20even%20the%20BJP%20have%20hopped%20on%20to%20the%20party%20for%20power.%20The%20party%20is%20bereft%20of%20any%20core%20ideology%2C%20so%20after%20Nitish%20retires%2C%20the%20JDU%20faces%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20split%2C%20with%20leaders%20switching%20to%20either%20the%20RJD%20or%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20has%20indicated%20that%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20(MGB)%20could%20fight%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20son%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20in%20state%20elections%20due%20in%202025.%20However%2C%20no%20one%20can%20really%20read%20what's%20on%20his%20mind.%20He%20may%20not%20give%20up%20the%20chair%20so%20easily%20(kissa%20kursi%20ka).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20has%20two%20most%20pressing%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHow%20he%20can%20ensure%20the%20JDU%20retains%20a%20maximum%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20party%20in%20the%202019%20elections%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHow%20he%20can%20ensure%20he%20remains%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20as%20long%20as%20he%20chooses%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20stay%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20has%20been%20flipping%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20RJD%20as%20he%20holds%20a%20crucial%2015%25-16%25%20vote%20share%20comprising%20largely%20of%20Kurmis%2C%20Koeris%2FKushwahas%2C%20Economically%20Backward%20Classes%20and%20Mahadalits%2C%20without%20which%20neither%20Lalu%20nor%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-Amit%20Shah%20duo%20can%20form%20a%20government%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20most%20of%20his%20party's%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20Nitish%20needs%20to%20make%20a%20gharwapsi%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA.%20But%20he%20does%20not%20share%20a%20good%20rapport%20with%20Modi-Shah.%20Besides%2C%20his%20credibility%20will%20dwindle%20further%2C%20as%20the%20unflattering%20moniker%20of%20%26quot%3Bpalturam%26quot%3B%20(flip-flop%20man)%20of%20Indian%20politics%20is%20reinforced.%20The%20BJP%20may%20not%20wish%20to%20take%20him%20back%20but%20for%20their%20Mission%20400%20in%202024%2C%20the%20NDA%20needs%20allies%20to%20sweep%20Bihar%20and%20bolster%20its%20numbers..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Congress%20party's%20poor%20showing%2C%20Nitish%20may%20well%20reconcile%20to%20his%20prime%20ministerial%20dreams%20shattered%20for%20good.%20This%20means%20a%20national%20presence%20may%20not%20matter%20to%20him%20anymore.%20And%20the%20second%20priority%20of%20how%20he%20remains%20chief%20minister%20till%202025%20and%20beyond%20attains%20greater%20importance.%20He%20may%20not%20trust%20the%20BJP%20for%20fear%20of%20a%20Shiv%20Sena-like%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20question%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar%20is%20-%20to%20whom%20does%20he%20want%20to%20pass%20on%20his%20legacy%20-%20BJP%20or%20RJD%3F%20The%20RJD%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20power%20and%20to%20enjoy%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20position%2C%20has%20to%20support%20Nitish%20unless%20it%20is%20able%20to%20break%20the%20JDU%2C%20which%20appears%20to%20be%20difficult%20at%20this%20stage.%20The%20RJD%2C%20though%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20flex%20its%20muscles%20closer%20to%20the%202025%20Bihar%20polls%2C%20with%20Lalu%20Yadav%20demanding%20chief%20ministership%20for%20son%20Tejashwi%20and%20pole%20position%20for%20him%20in%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20will%20be%2074%20years%20then%20and%20nearer%20to%20retirement%2C%20by%20some%20accounts%2C%20though%20people%20senior%20to%20him%2C%20like%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20and%20Pinayari%20Vijayan%2C%20still%20remain%20chief%20ministers.%20This%20could%20tempt%20him%20to%20bargain%20for%202025%20as%20his%20last%20election%20with%20the%20RJD%2C%20be%20the%20chief%20minister%20face%20again%2C%20hold%20the%20top%20post%20at%20least%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20if%20he%20wins%20and%20then%20hand%20over%20the%20mantle%20to%20Tejashwi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20the%20junior%20partner%20but%20still%20occupying%20the%20chief%20minister's%20chair%20makes%20an%20alliance%20with%20any%20party%20tricky%20for%20Nitish%2C%20with%20the%20RJD%20plus%20allies%20just%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20by%207%20seats.%20The%20Mahagatbandhan%20excluding%20JDU%20has%20115%20MLAs%3B%20NDA%20has%2082%2C%20JDU%20has%2045%20MLAs%20in%20a%20house%20of%20243%20where%20122%20is%20needed%20for%20a%20simple%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20the%20JDU%20hangs%20in%20the%20balance.%20Will%20Nitish%20remain%20in%20INDIA%20or%20rejoin%20the%20NDA%3F%20Will%20the%20BJP%20take%20back%20Nitish%20Kumar%20to%20bolster%20its%20Mission%20400%20prospects%3F%20Or%20will%20the%20JDU%20merge%20with%20RJD%20to%20prevent%20a%20split%20with%20the%20condition%20that%20he%20would%20be%20chief%20minister%20face%20in%202025%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17039112