ating%20from%20the%20state%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nicaragua-bound%20aircraft%2C%20an%20Airbus%20A340%20carrying%20276%20passengers%2C%20was%20grounded%20in%20France%20for%20four%20days%20over%20suspected%20human%20trafficking.%20It%20landed%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20December%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20state%20Crime%20Investigation%20Department%20(CID)%20official%2C%20those%20passengers%20included%20at%20least%2060%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20who%20have%20already%20reached%20their%20respective%20native%20places%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20being%20questioned%20by%20the%20department%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20they%20had%20any%20plans%20to%20cross%20into%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20illegally%20after%20reaching%20Latin%20America%2C%20the%20official%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20sent%20back%20from%20France.%20There%20was%20a%20rumour%20they%20had%20planned%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20illegally%20after%20landing%20in%20Nicaragua.%20In%20their%20statements%2C%20they%20told%20us%20they%20were%20going%20there%20as%20tourists.%20We%20are%20going%20into%20the%20details%20to%20find%20out%20who%20were%20the%20agents%20behind%20their%20trip%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20S%20P%20Rajkumar%2C%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20CID%20-%20Crime%20and%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2060%20who%20returned%2C%20some%2020%20have%20been%20grilled%20already%20by%20the%20agency%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20verifying%20their%20documents%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20they%20used%20genuine%20or%20forged%20documents%20to%20proceed%20to%20Central%20America.%20We%20will%20also%20check%20their%20financial%20transactions%20because%2C%20ideally%2C%20they%20should%20not%20have%20paid%20more%20if%20they%20were%20going%20there%20as%20normal%20tourists%20and%20not%20with%20any%20other%20intention%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20senior%20IPS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20we%20have%20started%20questioning%2C%20no%20one%20is%20divulging%20facts.%20They%20claim%20they%20went%20there%20as%20tourists.%20We%20are%20investigating%20the%20case%20from%20all%20angles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20CID%20(Crime)%2C%20Sanjay%20Kharat%20had%20said%20the%20CID%20had%20formed%20four%20teams%20to%20investigate%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CID%20(crime)%20wants%20to%20take%20action%20against%20agents%20who%20had%20promised%20help%20to%20the%20victims%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries%20(illegally).%20We%20have%20formed%20four%20teams%20which%20will%20get%20information%20from%20the%20victims%20regarding%20promises%20made%20to%20them%20by%20these%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chartered%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20operated%20by%20Romanian%20charter%20company%20Legend%20Airlines%20and%20bound%20for%20Nicaragua%2C%20landed%20at%20Vatry%20near%20Paris%20on%20December%2021%20for%20a%20technical%20stopover%20en%20route%20from%20Dubai%20when%20the%20French%20police%20intervened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20authorities%20launched%20a%20judicial%20investigation%20into%20the%20conditions%20and%20purpose%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20with%20a%20unit%20specialising%20in%20organised%20crime%20investigating%20suspected%20human%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENicaragua%20has%20become%20a%20popular%20destination%20for%20those%20seeking%20asylum%20in%20the%20US.%20As%20many%20as%2096%2C917%20Indians%20attempted%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20illegally%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202023%2C%20signalling%20a%2051.61%20per%20cent%20jump%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20according%20to%20data%20made%20available%20by%20the%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Patrol%20(CBP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2041%2C770%20of%20those%20Indians%20a