t%20and%20six%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20from%20the%20redeveloped%20Ayodhya%20Dham%20Railway%20Station%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20temple%20town%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmrit%20Bharat%20is%20a%20new%20category%20of%20superfast%20passenger%20trains%20equipped%20with%20the%20LHB%20push-pull%20feature.%20However%2C%20these%20trains%20come%20with%20non-air-conditioned%20coaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20train%20has%20locos%20at%20both%20ends%20for%20better%20acceleration.%20It%20provides%20improved%20facilities%20for%20rail%20passengers%2C%20like%20beautifully%20designed%20seats%2C%20better%20luggage%20racks%2C%20mobile%20charging%20points%20with%20suitable%20mobile%20holders%2C%20LED%20lights%2C%20CCTV%2C%20and%20a%20public%20information%20system%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Amrit%20Bharat%20trains%20that%20will%20ply%20as%20Darbhanga-Ayodhya-Anand%20Vihar%20Terminal%20Amrit%20Bharat%20Express%20and%20Malda%20Town-Sir%20M.%20Visvesvaraya%20Terminus%20(Bengaluru)%20Amrit%20Bharat%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20to%20be%20flagged%20off%20include%20Shri%20Mata%20Vaishno%20Devi%20Katra-New%20Delhi%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%3B%20Amritsar-Delhi%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%3B%20Coimbatore-Bangalore%20Cantt%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%3B%20Mangalore-Madgaon%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%3B%20Jalna-Mumbai%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%3B%20and%20Ayodhya-Anand%20Vihar%20Terminal%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20also%20dedicate%20to%20the%20nation%20three%20railway%20projects%20worth%20Rs%202300%20crore%20to%20strengthen%20rail%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20projects%20include%20the%20Rooma%20Chakeri-Chanderi%20third%20line%20project%3B%20the%20Jaunpur-Tulsi%20Nagar%2C%20Akbarpur-Ayodhya%2C%20Sohawal-Patranga%2C%20and%20Safdarganj-Rasauli%20sections%20of%20the%20Jaunpur-Ayodhya-Barabanki%20doubling%20project%3B%20and%20the%20doubl