-over-75-million-people-in-2023-but-population-growth-rate-is-slowing%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Forbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20November%202022%2C%20the%20U.N.%20estimated%20the%20world%20population%20reached%208%20billion%20people%2C%2011%20years%20after%20reaching%20the%207%20billion%20milestone%2C%20with%20UN%20Secretary%20General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20attributing%20population%20growth%20to%20%26quot%3Bscientific%20breakthroughs%20and%20improvements%20in%20nutrition%2C%20public%20health%2C%20and%20sanitation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20factors%20like%20decreasing%20fertility%20rates%20and%20a%20smaller%20proportion%20of%20young%20people%2C%20the%20Census%20Bureau%20anticipates%20that%20achieving%20a%20global%20population%20of%209%20billion%20will%20take%20slightly%20over%2014%20years.%20Furthermore%2C%20reaching%20the%2010%20billion%20mark%20is%20projected%20to%20take%20an%20additional%2016.4%20years%2C%20reflecting%20a%20decelerating%20growth%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20impacted%20population%20growth%20as%20well%2C%20with%20global%20life%20expectancy%20at%20birth%20falling%20to%2071%20years%20in%202021%20and%20countries%20experiencing%20unequal%20recovery%20from%20the%20pandemic%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20the%20new%20portal%20further%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703905560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-07%2Fpibti2h8_world-population-generic-bloomberg_625x300_15_July_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworlds-population-to-cross-8-billion-mark-on-jan-1-says-us-census-4767696%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20projected%20world%20population%20on%20January%201%2C%202024%2C%20is%208%2C019%2C876%2C189%2C%20an%20increase%20of%2075%2C162%2C541%20from%20New%20Year's%20Day%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworlds-population-to-cross-8-billion-mark-on