figure%3E%3Cp%3EMidgard%20has%20the%20largest%20variety%20of%20supernatural%20creatures%20in%20a%20Maas%20series%2C%20from%20faeries%20and%20merpeople%20to%20fauns%20and%20vampyrs.%20The%20non-human%20creatures%20are%20referred%20to%20as%20Vanir%2C%20and%20they%20develop%20powers%20such%20as%20centuries-long%20lifespans%20and%20super-hearing%20after%20they%20make%20the%20%26quot%3BDrop%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20burst%20of%20pure%20magic%20that%20helps%20power%20the%20planet's%20grid%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20planet%20is%20organized%20into%20four%20houses%2C%20and%20they're%20all%20home%20to%20multiple%20creatures%3A%20the%20House%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%2C%20the%20House%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%2C%20the%20House%20of%20Flame%20and%20Shadow%2C%20and%20the%20House%20of%20Many%20Waters.%20Humans%20belong%20to%20the%20House%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%2C%20while%20fae%20are%20members%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreatures%20called%20the%20Asteri%20rule%20over%20all%20of%20the%20Houses%20on%20Midgard%2C%20and%20the%20Archangels%20on%20the%20Imperial%20Senate%20do%20much%20of%20their%20day-to-day%20ruling%20as%20governors.%20Humans%20have%20historically%20been%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20Midgard's%20ranks%2C%20serving%20as%20slaves%20for%20other%20creatures%2C%20though%20they%20have%20gained%20a%20degree%20of%20freedom%20by%20the%20time%20the%20plot%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BCrescent%20City%26quot%3B%20series%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20Maas'%20story%20takes%20place%20in%20Crescent%20City%2C%20which%20is%20on%20a%20continent%20called%20Valbara%2C%20though%20the%20Asteri%20live%20in%20the%20Eternal%20City%20on%20Pangera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20%26quot%3BCrescent%20City%26quot%3B%20features%20modern%20technology%20alongside%20magic%2C%20unlike%20Maas'%20other%20series.%20The%20characters%20have%20cellphones%2C%20play%20modern%20sports%20like%20baseball%2C%20and%20attend%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EProtagonist%20Bryce%20Quinlan%20is%20heir%20to%20the%20Starborn%20fae%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryce%20reveals%20that%20she%20inherited%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20Starborn%20fae%2C%20so%20she%20can%20harness%20literal%20starlight%2C%20which%20is%20even%20more%20impressive%20considering%20her%20mother%20is%20human.%20She%20has%20an%20eight-pointed%20star%20on%20her%20chest%20to%20prove%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20she%20made%20the%20Drop%2C%20Bryce%20also%20gained%20power%20from%20everyone%20who%20had%20offered%20a%20drop%20of%20theirs%20to%20Crescent%20City%20in%20a%20fountain%2C%20giving%20her%20access%20to%20even%20more%20magic.%20She%20became%20more%20powerful%20than%20her%20brother%2C%20Prince%20Ruhn%20Danaan%2C%20and%20her%20father%2C%20the%20Autumn%20King%2C%20during%20her%20Drop%2C%20making%20her%20the%20heir%20to%20all%20the%20Starborn%20fae%20on%20Midgard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Bryce%20explores%20her%20power%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20discovers%20that%20she%20can%20teleport%20thanks%20to%20her%20Starborn%20lineage%2C%20and%20she%20can%20harness%20other%20fae's%20power%2C%20using%20her%20mate%20Hunt%20Athalar's%20lightning%20in%20the%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%20also%20has%20a%20magical%20horn%20on%20her%20back%2C%20as%20her%20friend%20Danika%20Fendyr%20had%20it%20turned%20into%20tattoo%20ink%20and%20placed%20on%20her%20skin%20without%20her%20knowledge%20when%20Bryce%20was%20drunk.%20The%20horn%20allows%20Bryce%20to%20open%20portals%20to%20other%20worlds%20%E2%80%94%20which%20becomes%20critical%20to%20the%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBryce's%20mate%2C%20Hunt%20Athalar%2C%20has%20a%20history%20of%20rebelling%20against%20the%20Archangels%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%20meets%20Hunt%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20archangel%20Micah%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20later%20killed%20by%20Bryce%20%E2%80%94%20forces%20them%20to%20investigate%20a%20murder%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHunt%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Orion%2C%20is%20a%20fallen%20angel%20with%20feathered%20wings%20and%20the%20power%20to%20control%20lightning.%20He%20fought%20against%20the%20Imperial%20Senate%20in%20a%20rebellion%20with%20his%20then-lover%20Shahar%20about%20200%20years%20before%20the%20plot%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood.%26quot%3B%20They%20lost%2C%20Shahar%20died%2C%20and%20Hunt%20was%20forced%20into%20slavery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20serving%20out%20his%20time%20as%20an%20assassin%20for%20Micah%20when%20the%20archangel%20forced%20him%20to%20work%20with%20Bryce.%20However%2C%20Micah%20sells%20him%20to%20Shahar's%20evil%20sister%2C%20Sandriel%2C%20after%20Hunt%20is%20caught%20trying%20to%20bolster%20the%20human%20rebel%20movement%20with%20other%20fallen%20angels.%20Hunt%20is%20freed%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Asteri%2C%20Rigelus%2C%20after%20Bryce%20saves%20Crescent%20City%20from%20demons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%20also%20publicly%20names%20Hunt%20as%20her%20mate%20at%20a%20ball%20during%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBryce's%20brother%2C%20Ruhn%20Danaan%2C%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20a%20rebel%20spy%2C%20and%20he's%20keeping%20a%20prophecy%20about%20himself%20secret%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERuhn%20is%20the%20Crown%20Prince%20of%20the%20Valbaran%20Fae%2C%20as%20his%20mother%20is%20married%20to%20the%20Autumn%20King.%20He%20can%20control%20light%20and%20shadows%20and%20speak%20telepathically%2C%20and%20he%20is%20considered%20the%20%26quot%3BChosen%20One%26quot%3B%20among%20the%20fae%2C%20as%20he%20pulled%20the%20famed%20Starsword%20from%20a%20cave%20during%20a%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20crown%20prince%2C%20Ruhn%20is%20expected%20to%20carry%20on%20his%20father's%20bloodline%2C%20but%20he%20fears%20for%20his%20future%20because%20the%20Oracle%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20royal%20bloodline%20shall%20end%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20working%20on%20repairing%20his%20relationship%20with%20Bryce%20throughout%20the%20series%20after%20the%20pair%20had%20a%20falling%20out%20when%20he%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20and%20Ruhn%20joins%20the%20rebel%20movement%20with%20Bryce%20and%20Hunt%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath.%26quot%3B%20Ruhn%20uses%20his%20telepathy%20to%20connect%20to%20a%20spy%20known%20as%20Agent%20Daybright%20(he%20calls%20the%20spy%20Day)%20after%20a%20rebel%20named%20Sofie%20dies%20and%20loses%20touch%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20start%20swapping%20information%2C%20and%20they%20develop%20a%20romantic%20connection%20without%20knowing%20who%20the%20other%20is%2C%20eventually%20becoming%20intimate%20through%20their%20minds.%20When%20he%20gets%20caught%20breaking%20into%20the%20Asteri's%20palace%20with%20Bryce%2C%20Ruhn%20discovers%20that%20Day%20is%20Lidia%20Cervos%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Hind%2C%20a%20spy-hunter%20for%20the%20Asteri.%20Though%20she%20is%20a%20double%20agent%20trying%20to%20overthrow%20them%2C%20Ruhn%20sees%20her%20true%20identity%20as%20a%20betrayal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERuhn%20helps%20Bryce%20escape%20the%20Asteri%2C%20giving%20her%20the%20Starsword%20and%20telling%20her%20about%20the%20Oracle's%20prophecy%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BHOSAB.%26quot%3B%20But%20he%20is%20taken%20prisoner%20by%20the%20Asteri%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Lidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBryce%20discovered%20the%20Asteri%20are%20parasites%20at%20the%20climax%20of%20'House%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath'%20%E2%80%94%20and%20fled%20to%20another%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%26quot%3B%20by%20Sarah%20J.%20Maas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652420506561dd877e74aa04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBloomsbury%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBryce%2C%20Hunt%2C%20and%20Ruhn%20break%20into%20the%20Asteri%20Archives%20at%20their%20palace%20in%20the%20Eternal%20City%20after%20seeing%20a%20video%20of%20Sofie%20going%20into%20them%20before%20her%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20mission%2C%20Bryce%20discovers%20the%20Asteri%20are%20not%20gods%20like%20everyone%20thinks.%20They're%20parasitic%20aliens%20who%20have%20conquered%20hundreds%20of%20planets%2C%20stealing%20magic%20from%20the%20beings%20that%20inhabit%20them%2C%20and%20they%20have%20been%20stuck%20on%20Midgard%20after%20trying%20and%20failing%20to%20conquer%20Hel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20Vanir%20are%20not%20a%20different%20species.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20all%20types%20of%20fae%20from%20different%20planets%20that%20the%20Asteri%20brought%20to%20Midgard.%20They%20brainwashed%20them%20into%20thinking%20they%20originated%20there%20to%20give%20themselves%20a%20food%20source%2C%20using%20the%20first%20and%20second%20light%20the%20fae%20offer%20as%20sustenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERigelus%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Asteri%2C%20then%20reveals%20he%20wanted%20Bryce%20to%20discover%20the%20truth%20so%20she%20would%20open%20a%20portal%20to%20the%20planet%20her%20species%20of%20fae%20originally%20came%20from%2C%20as%20the%20Asteri%20were%20overthrown%20on%20the%20unnamed%20world%20and%20want%20to%20taste%20the%20planet's%20magic%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20acquiescing%2C%20Bryce%20flees%20and%20tries%20to%20open%20a%20portal%20to%20Hel%2C%20hoping%20her%20friend%20Aidas%2C%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20princes%20of%20Hel%2C%20can%20help%20her.%20She%20ends%20up%20in%20Prythian%2C%20the%20land%20from%20%26quot%3BA%20Court%20of%20Thorns%20and%20Roses%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20Rhysand%2C%20the%20High%20Lord%20of%20the%20Night%20Court%2C%20introducing%20himself%20to%20her%20in%20the%20novel's%20final%20scene%20in%20the%20language%20of%20the%20ancient%20fae%20as%20his%20Inner%20Circle%20looks%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20fae%20from%20'A%20Court%20of%20Thorns%20and%20Roses'%20look%20familiar%20to%20Bryce%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20Rhysand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Bryce%20arrives%20in%20Prythian%2C%20she%20notes%20several%20similarities%20between%20the%20fae%20she%20meets%20and%20those%20she%20knows%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20describes%20Amren%20as%20having%20%26quot%3Bangular%20eyes%20like%20Fury's%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20close%20friend%20in%20Crescent%20City%20with%20a%20classified%20Vanir%20category.%20She%20also%20notes%20that%20characters%20who%20seem%20to%20be%20Feyre%2C%20the%20High%20Lady%20of%20the%20Night%20Court%2C%20and%20her%20sister%20Nesta%20to%20%26quot%3BACOTAR%26quot%3B%20fans%20have%20pointed%20ears%20like%20the%20fae%20she%20is%20familiar%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20Rhysand's%20appearance%20that%20startles%20her%20most%2C%20as%20he%20looks%20exactly%20like%20Ruhn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20eyes%20were%20the%20same%20shade%20of%20violet%20blue%20as%20Ruhn's%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BHis%20short%20hair%20the%20same%20gleaming%20black.%20This%20male's%20skin%20was%20browner%2C%20but%20the%20face%2C%20the%20posture%E2%80%A6it%20was%20her%20brother's.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaas%20has%20yet%20to%20detail%20the%20significance%20of%20Ruhn%20and%20Rhysand's%20similar%20appearances%2C%20but%20she%20did%20reveal%20that%20Bryce's%20Starsword%20is%20Gwydion%2C%20a%20weapon%20long%20lost%20in%20Prythian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Amren%20explains%20to%20Nesta%20in%20%26quot%3BA%20Court%20of%20Silver%20Flames%2C%26quot%3B%20Gwydion%20was%20dipped%20in%20the%20cauldron%20as%20it%20was%20welded%2C%20giving%20it%20special%20powers.%20It's%20also%20a%20companion%20to%20Truth%20Teller%2C%20a%20blade%20Azriel%20carries%2C%20and%20the%20two%20weapons%20light%20up%20when%20they're%20placed%20next%20to%20each%20other%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BHOSAB.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETharion%20Ketos%20made%20it%20out%20of%20the%20confrontation%20with%20the%20Asteri%20alive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Asteri%20took%20Ruhn%20and%20Hunt%20prisoner%20after%20they%20broke%20into%20the%20archives%2C%20Tharion%2C%20a%20mer%2C%20managed%20to%20escape%20after%20he%20and%20Cormac%20Donnall%2C%20the%20Crown%20Prince%20of%20the%20Avallen%20Fae%20and%20a%20rebel%20fighter%2C%20distracted%20the%20Asteri%20during%20the%20break-in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECormac%20sacrificed%20himself%20to%20let%20Tharion%20escape%2C%20making%20Tharion%20the%20only%20person%20who%20physically%20went%20to%20the%20palace%20with%20Bryce's%20team%20to%20make%20it%20out%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETharion%20had%20also%20made%20a%20deal%20to%20serve%20the%20Viper%20Queen%20before%20joining%20the%20mission%20to%20save%20himself%20after%20he%20told%20the%20River%20Princess%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20marry%20her%2C%20as%20he%20feared%20her%20mother%2C%20the%20River%20Queen%2C%20would%20take%20revenge%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIthan%20Holstrom%2C%20a%20wolf%20shifter%2C%20saved%20a%20mystic%20who%20could%20shake%20up%20the%20pack%20rankings%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20book%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIthan%2C%20a%20wolf%20shifter%2C%20is%20Connor%20Holstrom's%20younger%20brother.%20Connor%20was%20Danika's%20second%20in%20command%2C%20and%20he%20and%20Bryce%20were%20about%20to%20start%20dating%20before%20he%20died%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Earth%20and%20Blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIthan%20and%20Bryce%20were%20close%20friends%20before%20the%20pack's%20murder%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20harbored%20secret%20romantic%20feelings%20for%20her%20%E2%80%94%20but%20when%20he%20saw%20texts%20that%20revealed%20she%20hooked%20up%20with%20someone%20else%20the%20night%20Connor%20died%2C%20Ithan%20cut%20Bryce%20off%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they're%20reunited%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Sky%20and%20Breath%26quot%3B%20after%20Ithan%20is%20kicked%20out%20of%20his%20pack%20for%20defending%20Bryce%2C%20and%20he%20starts%20working%20with%20her%20group.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIthan%20later%20stumbles%20upon%20a%20wolf%20when%20he%20and%20Bryce%20visit%20the%20mystics%20in%20search%20of%20information%20about%20the%20afterlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ithan%20tells%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20wolves%20about%20it%2C%20he%20implies%20that%20she%20is%20the%20lost%20Fendyr%20heir%20who%20could%20unite%20the%20wolf%20packs.%20In%20the%20epilogue%20of%20%26quot%3BHOSAB%2C%26quot%3B%20Ithan%20steals%20the%20unnamed%20mystic%20away%20in%20hopes%20of%20protecting%20her%20and%20saving%20the%20wolf%20shifters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsarah-j-maas-crescent-city-details-to-remember-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703890253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6515bdcdc50dce001913510b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsarah-j-maas-crescent-city-details-to-remember-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20third%20book%20in%20Sarah%20J.%20Maas'%20%26quot%3BCrescent%20City%26quot%3B%20series%20comes%20out%20January%2030.%20Here's%20what%20to%20remember%20before%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Flame%20and%20Shadow%26quot%3B%20is%20released.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgrindell%40businessinsider.com%20(Samantha%20Grindell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsarah-j-maas-crescent-city-details-to-remember-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tim%20Burton%E2%80%99s%20Unmade%20%E2%80%98Catwoman%E2%80%99%20Was%20an%20%E2%80%98%2418%20Million%20Black-and-White%20Movie%2C%E2%80%99%20Says%20%E2%80%98Batman%20Returns%E2%80%99%20Writer%3A%20Selina%20Kyle%20%E2%80%98Low-Key%20Living%20in%20a%20Small%20Town%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703889438000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2