rd%20in%20foreground%20with%20cruise%20ship%20in%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f1fafec62ab5daf7faecd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Anthony%20McWilliams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthony%20McWilliams%20has%20been%20chronicling%20his%20travels%20on%20the%209-month%20Ultimate%20World%20Cruise%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMcWilliams%20got%20off%20the%20ship%20in%20Grenada%20and%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20reboard%20until%20the%20ship%20docks%20in%20Uruguay.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrazilian%20port%20law%20does%20not%20allow%20travelers%20to%20disembark%20and%20rejoin%20a%20cruise%20at%20a%20different%20port.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20TikTok%20fervor%2C%20there%20have%20been%20very%20few%20actual%20moments%20of%20drama%20from%20the%209-month%20Ultimate%20World%20Cruise%20excursion%20that%20set%20off%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Antoine%20McWilliams%20is%20the%20exception%20to%20that%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcWilliams%20signed%20up%20for%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20Ultimate%20World%20Cruise%20in%202021%20as%20a%20solo%20traveler%2C%20taking%20the%20trip%20in%20memory%20of%20his%20late%20husband%20Michael%2C%20who%20died%20of%20cancer%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20died%2C%20Michael%20made%20McWilliams%20promise%20to%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20'Travel%20will%20be%20your%20sanity%2C%20travel%20will%20be%20your%20salvation.'%20And%20that's%20exactly%20what%20I've%20done%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years%20is%20travel%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20McWilliams%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22couple%20kissing%20under%20a%20pergola%20on%20the%20beach%20getting%20married%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f275bec62ab5daf7fb207%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcWilliams%20and%20his%20late%20husband%20Michael%20Smith%20getting%20married%20on%20the%20beach%20in%202016.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Anthony%20McWilliams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2054-year-old%20retired%20public%20health%20project%20coordinator%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20side%20trip%20to%20Brazil%20during%20the%20cruise%20to%20visit%20friends%20and%20some%20of%20the%20special%20places%20he%20and%20Michael%20had%20traveled%20to%20in%20past%20years%2C%20so%20he%20asked%20ship%20officials%20for%20approval%20to%20leave%20the%20ship%20at%20one%20stop%20and%20then%20hop%20back%20on%20a%20few%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20official%20policy%2C%20guests%20are%20allowed%20to%20hop%20off%20at%20one%20port%20and%20reboard%20at%20another.%20It's%20called%20%26quot%3Bdownlining%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20must%20be%20requested%20in%20advance%20(because%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20cruise%20ships%20hold%20on%20to%20passengers'%20passports%20while%20on%20board).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20each%20country%20has%20different%20policies%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20disembarking%20and%20rejoining%20a%20trip%2C%20and%20Royal%20Caribbean%20told%20him%20Brazil%20would%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20disembark%20at%20one%20port%20and%20then%20get%20back%20on%20at%20another.%20BI%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20instead%2C%20McWilliams%20said%20he%20disembarked%20in%20Grenada%2C%20missing%20the%20ship's%20planned%20port%20in%20French%20Guyana%2C%20and%20plans%20to%20reboard%20the%20ship%20when%20it%20docks%20in%20Montevideo%2C%20Uruguay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%3F%20That%20won't%20be%20until%20January%204%2C%202024.%20McWilliams%20has%20some%20time%20to%20kill%20on%20land%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrazil%20is%20my%20favorite%20place%20to%20visit.%20I%20love%20it%20here.%20It's%20so%20scenic.%20And%20then%20again%2C%20my%20very%20first%20time%20coming%20to%20Brazil%20was%20in%202007%20%E2%80%94%20my%20husband%20Michael%20brought%20me%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20walk%20the%20streets%20of%20Brazil%20and%20remember%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcWilliams%20chose%20to%20disembark%20in%20Grenada%20because%20flights%20to%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro%20were%20about%20%241%2C000%20cheaper%20than%20from%20French%20Guyana.%20But%20it%20turned%20out%20the%20ship%20had%20been%20unable%20to%20dock%20in%20French%20Guyana%20because%20of%20bad%20weather%20anyway.%20Had%20he%20stayed%20in%20French%20Guyana%2C%20he%20would%20have%20never%20been%20able%20to%20make%20a%20flight.%20McWilliams%20considers%20it%20kismet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGod%20worked%20in%20mysterious%20ways%20because%20I'm%20not%20on%20the%20ship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22group%20of%20four%20people%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20a%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f27c91c5c7b8c9a0cfdfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22967%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcWilliams%20with%20a%20few%20of%20the%20friends%20he's%20made%20on%20the%20Ultimate%20World%20Cruise.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Anthony%20McWilliams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20not%20being%20able%20to%20board%20the%20ship%20again%20for%20about%20a%20week%20McWilliams%20plans%20to%20meet%20his%20Ultimate%20World%20Cruise%20friends%20for%20an%20excursion%20to%20Christ%20the%20Redeemer%20statue%20in%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20kind%20of%20sad%20in%20a%20way%20that%20I'm%20even%20going%20to%20go%20to%20the%20ship%20and%20meet%20them%2C%20but%20I%20just%20can't%20go%20on%20the%20boat.%20It's%20such%20a%20crazy%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcWilliams%20said%20he's%20enjoying%20his%20time%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20love%20to%20believe%20that%20I%20had%20figured%20life%20out%2C%20but%20it's%20because%20of%20my%20husband%20that%20I%20am%20able%20to%20do%20this%20trip%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20older%20we%20get%2C%20the%20less%20mobile%20we%20may%20get%2C%20and%20I%20want%20do%20it%20now.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20these%20kind%20of%20moves%20and%20see%20the%20world%20when%20I'm%20able%20to%20actually%20really%20enjoy%20it%20in%20my%20body%20and%20in%20my%20spirit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultimate-world-cruise-passenger-cant-re-board-ship-in-brazil-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703884514000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f27181c5c7b8c9a0cfd95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultimate-world-cruise-passenger-cant-re-board-ship-in-brazil-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthony%20McWilliams%20is%20on%20the%209-month%20Ultimate%20World%20Cruise%20but%20he's%20been%20grounded%20until%20January%204.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jgerstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Julie%20Gerstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A124%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultimate-world-cruise-passenger-cant-re-board-ship-in-brazil-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20stocks%20fall%20but%20end%20the%20year%20with%20big%20gains%20as%20traders%20look%20ahead%20to%20easier%20Fed%20policy%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stock%20trader%20happy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd9e50d6524f10019792484%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20stock%20market%20was%20up%20big%20in%202023.%3Cp%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStocks%20ended%20the%20final%20trading%20session%20of%20the%20year%20lower%20but%20logged%20strong%20gains%20for%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20stopped%20just%20shy%20of%20a%20new%20all-time%20high%20but%20gained%2024%25%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETraders%20are%20laying%20bets%20that%20the%20Fed%20cuts%20interest%20rates%20as%20early%20as%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20stocks%20finished%20the%20last%20trading%20of%20the%20session%20lower%2C%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20failing%20to%20secure%20a%20new%20all-time%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20an%20annual%20basis%2C%20the%20stock%20market%20enjoyed%20a%20stellar%20performance%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20gained%2024%25%2C%20powered%20by%20resilient%20consumer%20spending%2C%20an%20economy%20that%20bucked%20calls%20for%20a%20recession%2C%20and%20steady%20corporate%20profits.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20was%20powered%20higher%2C%20too%2C%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20rode%20a%20wave%20of%20enthusiasm%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20finish%20the%20year%2044%25%20higher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20were%20volatile%20but%20moved%20steadily%20higher%20throughout%20the%20year.%20Some%20of%20the%20strongest%20gains%20came%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20as%20traders%20began%20placing%20bets%20that%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20was%20about%20done%20raising%20rates%20and%20looking%20toward%20loosening%20monetary%20policy%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20series%20of%20encouraging%20inflation%20reports%20that%20showed%20price%20increases%20were%20slowing%2C%20Fed%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%20made%20a%20long-awaited%20nod%20to%20a%20policy%20pivot%20at%20the%20December%20meeting.%20Officials%20indicated%20that%20three%20rate%20cuts%20may%20be%20coming%20next%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-slow