or%20lounging%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-t-shirt-men%5C%22%3EBrooklinen%20Prospect%20Tee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%2050%25%20modal%20and%2050%25%20cotton.%20At%2095%25%20modal%20and%205%25%20spandex%2C%20the%20JamTee%20is%20the%20only%20loungewear%20T-shirt%20that%20I've%20tested%20so%20far%20that%20outshines%20it%20in%20comfort%20and%20softness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Long%20Jambys%20are%20made%20with%20the%20same%20blend%20of%20materials%2C%20and%20are%20just%20as%20comfortable%20as%20the%20JamTee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20the%20Jambys%20Air%20JamTee%20with%20light%20shining%20through%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63530660ffcac3001876cf1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Air%20JamTee%20is%20basically%20see-through%2C%20so%20it's%20great%20for%20hot%20sleepers%20who%20prefer%20lightweight%20materials.%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20half%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20original%20JamTee%2C%20the%20Air%20JamTee%20is%20see-through%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20black.%20If%20you're%20going%20for%20a%20lighter%20color%2C%20it's%20worth%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20it%20will%20likely%20be%20more%20transparent%20than%20the%20black%20color.%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20wearing%20the%20Air%20JamTee%20during%20the%20summer%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20lounging%20around%20the%20house%20shirtless%2C%20but%20I%20probably%20wouldn't%20wear%20it%20outside%20as%20a%20normal%20T-shirt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20washed%20and%20dried%20all%20three%20items%20several%20times%20and%20they've%20held%20up%20very%20well.%20My%20only%20gripe%20is%20how%20easily%20they%20wrinkle%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20lounging%20around%20at%20home%2C%20that's%20the%20least%20of%20my%20concerns.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EUPDATE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20It's%20been%20over%20a%20year%20since%20I%20first%20tested%20Jambys%20and%20the%20pieces%20I%20tried%20have%20held%20up%20incredibly%20well.%20There%20still%20as%20soft%20and%20stretchy%20as%20they%20were%20when%20I%20first%20got%20them%2C%20and%20I've%20continued%20to%20wash%20and%20dry%20them%20without%20any%20major%20shrinkage%20or%20deterioration.%20I've%20yet%20to%20find%20more%20comfortable%20loungewear%20since%20discovering%20Jambys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESally's%20Review%20of%20Jambys%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20images.%20On%20the%20left%2C%20a%20woman%20takes%20a%20mirror%20selfie%20wearing%20green%20Jambys%20shorts%20and%20a%20t-shirt.%20On%20the%20right%2C%20a%20closeup%20of%20the%20waistband%20of%20the%20shorts%2C%20with%20the%20text%20'Jambys'%20printed%20on%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6353074f390dfe00196d8076%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeft%3A%20Sally%20wearing%20Jambys%20shorts%20and%20JamTee.%20Right%3A%20A%20closeup%20of%20the%20waist%20band%20for%20the%20Jamby%20shorts.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20sucker%20for%20all%20things%20soft%20and%20cozy.%20I've%20tested%20pajamas%20and%20loungewear%20from%20tons%20of%20brands%20for%20my%20job%2C%20but%20Jambys%20might%20just%20top%20the%20list.%20Shorts%20are%20a%20hard%20type%20of%20loungewear%2Fpajama%20bottom%20to%20get%20right%20because%20most%20styles%20made%20for%20women%20sit%20right%20at%20the%20butt%20cheek%20and%20most%20styles%20made%20for%20men%20are%20too%20long.%20The%20Jambys%20shorts%20are%20a%20perfect%20in-between%20length%2C%20and%20the%20ultra-stretchy%20elastic%20waistband%20doesn't%20dig%20into%20my%20stomach%2C%20which%20is%20a%20huge%20turn-off%20with%20pajama%20shorts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20JamTee%20is%20equally