5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20baby%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeeding%20more%20room%20for%20my%20family%2C%20and%20no%20longer%20feeling%20tethered%20to%20New%20York's%20exorbitant%20rental%20prices%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20started%20brainstorming%20where%20we%20might%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20considered%20my%20home%20state%20of%20Connecticut%2C%20but%20couldn't%20find%20a%20home%20to%20buy%20that%20didn't%20need%20many%20repairs%2C%20and%20longed%20to%20give%20up%20the%20Northeast's%20long%20dreary%20winters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20kept%20coming%20back%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-hotels-palm-springs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPalm%20Springs%2C%20California%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20the%20place%20we%20loved%20to%20vacation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Frivieria-becomes-margaritaville-palms-springs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhere%20we%20got%20married%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20always%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWouldn't%20it%20be%20cool%20to%20live%20here%20if%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20be%20in%20New%20York%20for%20work%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20monthlong%20visit%20during%20the%20summer%20to%20test%20out%20the%20intense%20heat%20and%20look%20at%20houses%2C%20we%20had%20an%20offer%20accepted%20on%20a%20home%2C%20and%20two-and-a-half%20years%20later%2C%20we're%20still%20happy%20Coachella%20Valley%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn't%20know%20anyone%20when%20we%20moved%20here%2C%20and%20many%20things%20continue%20to%20surprise%20us%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Palm%20Springs%20area%20isn't%20just%20for%20old%20people.%20Since%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20moved%20here%2C%20we've%20made%20so%20many%20friends%20with%20young%20kids.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20child%20wearing%20a%20yellow%20hat%20sits%20on%20the%20grass%20with%20the%20mountains%20in%20the%20distance.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f153dec62ab5daf7fa91d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20daughter%20at%20a%20park.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20friends%20learned%20we%20were%20moving%20near%20Palm%20Springs%2C%20we%20were%20always%20met%20with%20the%20same%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsn't%20it%20for%20old%20people%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20arrived%20to%20live%20here%20full-time%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20too.%20Initially%2C%20I%20wasn't%20worried.%20After%2010%20years%20in%20New%20York%2C%20I%20was%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20crowds%20and%20noise.%20Living%20like%20a%20retiree%20among%20palm%20trees%20and%20sparkling%20pools%20in%20my%20late%2030s%20sounded%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20Coachella%20Valley%20has%20long%20had%20a%20reputation%20as%20a%20retirement%20enclave%2C%20since%20living%20here%2C%20I%20know%20that%20that's%20just%20one%20demographic%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20shocking%20things%20has%20been%20how%20many%20new%20connections%20we've%20made%2C%20perhaps%20even%20more%20than%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20of%20families%20is%20smaller%20than%20in%20a%20big%20metro%20area%20and%20everyone%20seems%20to%20know%20everyone%2C%20so%20being%20a%20parent%20has%20made%20it%20incredibly%20easy%20to%20make%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20many%20other%20parents%20we've%20met%20%E2%80%94%20through%20my%20daughter's%20school%2C%20Facebook%20mom%20groups%2C%20and%20at%20the%20playground%20%E2%80%94%20are%20around%20the%20same%20age%2C%20and%20relocated%20from%20cities%20like%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Chicago%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco%20to%20work%20from%20home%20with%20a%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20at%20a%20cheaper%20price%2C%20just%20like%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20there%20are%20still%20plenty%20of%20%26quot%3Bsnowbirds%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20lot%20operates%20on%20a%20seasonal%20basis%20around%20this%20community.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20desert%20landscape%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f10c3ab6f2ebb11f7d28b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELooking%20over%20the%20Coachella%20Valley.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20living%20here%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20a%20retirement%20community%20to%20me%2C%20there%20is%20a%20noticeable%20shift%20every%20year%20around%20November%2C%20and%20again%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20the%20%26quot%3Bsnowbirds%26quot%3B%20return%2C%20and%20then%20leave%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20influx%20of%20young%20families%2C%20many%20homeowners%20and%20visitors%20to%20the%20area%20are%20still%20retirees%20who%20come%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bseason%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20typically%20November%20to%20May%2C%20when%20the%20weather%20feels%20near%20perfect.%20They%20get%20to%20drop%20in%20for%20the%20best%20time%20of%20the%20year%20and%20depart%20just%20before%20the%20long%2C%20dreadful%20summer%20when%20temperatures%20can%20reach%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.desertsun.com%2Fstory%2Fweather%2F2023%2F07%2F21%2Fpalm-springs-area-could-reach-record-high-of-120-degrees-friday%2F70445464007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E120%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20many%20businesses%20close%20until%20the%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20snowbirds%20return%2C%20I%20notice%20a%20huge%20uptick%20in%20local%20traffic%2C%20restaurant%20reservations%20are%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20secure%2C%20and%20local%20stores%20become%20inundated%20with%20long%20checkout%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20feels%20frustrating%20to%20me%20as%20a%20full-time%20resident%2C%20but%20their%20annual%20departure%20is%20a%20silver%20lining%20of%20living%20here%20during%20the%20hot%20summer%20when%20things%20feel%20calm%20and%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20in%20all%20honesty%2C%20I'm%20just%20envious.%20One%20day%20I%20hope%20I%20can%20be%20a%20snowbird%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELiving%20near%20the%20Coachella%20Valley%20Music%20and%20Arts%20Festival%20isn't%20as%20annoying%20as%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22coachella%202023%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643ad8e956f0dc0019894df8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoachella%20is%20a%20famous%20music%20festival%20in%20Indio%2C%20California.%3Cp%3ECallie%20Ahlgrim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20year%20I%20lived%20here%2C%20I%20dreaded%20the%20arrival%20of%20April%20and%2C%20with%20it%2C%20the%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthings-should-never-do-at-coachella-biggest-mistakes-from-local%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoachella%20Valley%20Music%20and%20Arts%20Festival%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feared%20the%20worst%20with%20raucous%20short-term%20vacation%20renters%2C%20loud%20parties%2C%20and%20traffic%20detours.%20Luckily%2C%20we've%20had%20no%20such%20problems%2C%20despite%20living%20not%20too%20far%20from%20the%20festival%20grounds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20always%20look%20forward%20to%20seeing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcoachella-festival-fashion-through-the-years-photos-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efestivalgoers'%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20year%20as%20they%20board%20shuttle%20buses%20at%20a%20hotel%20near%20my%20home%20or%20stock%20up%20on%20goods%20at%20my%20local%20Target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20big%20reason%20we%20wanted%20to%20move%20here%20was%20the%20access%20to%20the%20outdoors%20and%20hiking.%20We%20rarely%20go.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20and%20her%20baby%20next%20to%20large%20palm%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f11bb1c5c7b8c9a0cf2cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20on%20an%20attempted%20hike%20with%20her%20child.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20when%20it%20was%20just%20me%20and%20my%20husband%20vacationing%20here%2C%20our%20favorite%20thing%20to%20do%20was%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20Coachella%20Valley%20is%20full%20of%20trails%2C%20and%20Joshua%20Tree%20National%20Park%20is%20under%20an%20hour%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20residents%2C%20we%20imagined%20we'd%20hike%20every%20week.%20Our%20kids%20had%20other%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20we%20have%20two%20children%2C%20our%20life%20operates%20around%20their%20daily%20needs%20and%20desires.%20As%20most%20parents%20know%2C%20that%20hardly%20ever%20matches%20up%20with%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20toddler%20doesn't%20have%20the%20attention%20span%20or%20interest%20in%20a%20hike.%20At%20best%2C%20we%20can%20agree%20to%20a%20short%20%26quot%3Bnature%20walk%26quot%3B%20before%20she%20inevitably%20wants%20me%20to%20carry%20her%2030-pound%20body%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20save%20hikes%20for%20days%20when%20my%20parents%20can%20babysit%2C%20but%20it's%20far%20from%20every%20week%2C%20more%20like%20once%20every%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20were%20spoiled%20by%20food%20in%20New%20York.%20Especially%20takeout.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bowl%20of%20pasta%20and%20two%20spoons.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f1277ab6f2ebb11f7d375%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222755%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20meal%20the%20author%20prepared%20instead%20of%20ordering%20takeout.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20knew%20we%20had%20access%20to%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbest-restaurants-in-nyc-places-to-eat-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20restaurants%20in%20the%20world%20in%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20until%20I%20moved%20away%20that%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20I%20took%20that%20for%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20found%20restaurants%20in%20the%20Palm%20Springs%20area%20that%20we%20like%2C%20but%20the%20takeout%20scene%20feels%20especially%20bleak%20with%20limited%2C%20overpriced%2C%20and%20bland%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20long%20for%20my%20favorite%20Chinese%20food%2C%20Indian%20curries%2C%20and%20wood-fired%20pizza%20that%20was%20once%20just%20a%20Seamless%20order%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20usually%20rather%20cook%20as%20most%20places%20we've%20tried%20to%20go%20are%20disappointing.%20That%20always%20feels%20frustrating%20when%20I'm%20tired%20or%20returning%20from%20a%20trip%20and%20the%20last%20thing%20I%20want%20to%20do%20is%20fire%20up%20the%20stove.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20big-brand%20stores%20are%20only%20a%20mile%20away%2C%20making%20every%20day%20errands%20incredibly%20convenient.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20a%20Target%20store%20next%20to%20a%20mountain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f1e081c5c7b8c9a0cf97f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Target%20store%20in%20La%20Quinta%2C%20CA.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20I%20had%20to%20drive%20about%2045%20minutes%20to%20get%20to%20the%20closest%20Home%20Depot%20or%20Target.%20Similarly%20in%20New%20York%2C%20those%20stores%20were%20a%20lengthy%20subway%20ride%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20they're%20down%20the%20street.%20I%20can%20easily%20hit%20up%20Costco%2C%20Trader%20Joe's%2C%20Whole%20Foods%2C%20and%20Walmart.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20Lowe's%2C%20Home%20Depot%2C%20Home%20Goods%2C%20and%20Best%20Buy%20%E2%80%94%20it%20feels%20like%20every%20major%20chain%20has%20an%20outpost%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20welcome%20surprise%20when%20we%20moved%20in%20and%20had%20a%20whole%20house%20to%20furnish%20and%20maintain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20appreciate%20it%20now%20when%20I%20realize%20I've%20forgotten%20a%20single%20grocery%20item%2C%20or%20it's%20hot%20outside%20and%20a%20trip%20to%20Target%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20entertain%20an%20antsy%20toddler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20miss%20many%20things%20about%20the%20Northeast%2C%20I%20know%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20this%20kind%20of%20convenience%20in%20the%20other%20places%20we%20considered%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOther%20things%20are%20incredibly%20inconvenient%2C%20such%20as%20childcare%20and%20healthcare.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222979%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22childcare%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d0298b36fc92002a646db98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222178%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChildren%20at%20a%20daycare.%3Cp%3EThomas%20Kienzle%2F%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20I%20talk%20about%20most%20with%20fellow%20parents%20here%20is%20how%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20Coachella%20Valley%20lacks%20the%20infrastructure%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20all%20the%20new%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20on%20our%20third%20pediatrician%20in%20two%20years%20because%20it's%20been%20impossible%20to%20find%20a%20doctor%20who%20doesn't%20have%20a%206-month%20wait%20for%20appointments%2C%20or%20sees%20kids%20same-day%20when%20they're%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20our%20first%20two%20doctors%2C%20every%20time%20my%20daughter%20had%20an%20illness%2C%20even%20a%20minor%20ear%20infection%2C%20we%20were%20always%20told%2C%20%26quot%3BSorry%2C%20go%20to%20ER.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20we%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20concierge-style%20doctor%20with%20a%20%24250%20annual%20fee%20per%20child%20that%20we%20are%20now%20guaranteed%20visits%20and%20after-hours%20messaging%20for%20emergencies.%20All%20of%20those%20services%20were%20standard%20in%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20I%20know%20all%20face%20the%20same%20problem%2C%20and%20the%20doctors%20I've%20spoken%20with%20say%20there%20just%20aren't%20enough%20providers%20to%20meet%20the%20number%20of%20kids%20living%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20say%20the%20same%20for%20local%20childcare.%20Most%20daycares%20and%20preschools%20I've%20encountered%20are%20for%20ages%202%20and%20up%2C%20with%20long%20waitlists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20oldest%2C%20we%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20hire%20a%20nanny%20until%20she%20became%20eligible%20for%20the%20one%20school%20with%20a%20spot%20open.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20schools%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20and%20a%20half-hour%20drive%20from%20our%20house.%20This%20means%20we%20spend%20two%20hours%20a%20day%20driving%20back%20and%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20closer-to-home%20school%20with%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20infant%20rooms%20has%20had%20us%20on%20a%20waitlist%20for%20over%20a%20year%20for%20our%20baby%2C%20but%20I%20fear%20we'll%20be%20paying%20for%20a%20nanny%20until%20she%20turns%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20researched%20childcare%20centers%20and%20medical%20practices%20before%20moving%20here%20and%20saw%20well-reviewed%20options%2C%20but%20we%20had%20no%20idea%20there%20would%20be%20so%20many%20waitlists%20and%20disappointing%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOwning%20a%20pool%20is%20not%20as%20fun%20as%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pool%20at%20sunset%20with%20a%20hat%20on%20the%20ledge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f169dec62ab5daf7fa9f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20pool.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Hochberg%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20looked%20at%20houses%20here%2C%20I%20refused%20to%20consider%20one%20without%20a%20pool.%20It%20was%20a%20must%20given%20the%20heat%2C%20I%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20wrong.%20Owning%20a%20pool%20is%20a%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeating%20it%20takes%20about%2024%20hours%20and%20after%20friends%20told%20me%20it%20can%20cost%20them%20%24100-%24300%20to%20heat%20it%20each%20time%2C%20we%20avoided%20using%20it%20altogether%20in%20the%20winter.%20My%20kids%20never%20want%20to%20go%20in%20for%20more%20than%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20time%20to%20use%20it%2C%20so%20the%20cost%20is%20hardly%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%2C%20the%20extreme%20heat%20makes%20it%20feel%20like%20bathwater%2C%20so%20we%20only%20use%20it%20a%20handful%20of%20times%20then%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaintenance%20is%20also%20expensive.%20I%20pay%20%24180%20per%20month%20for%20twice-a-week%20cleanings%20for%20a%20pool%20I%20rarely%20use.%20The%20pool%20pump%20also%20broke%20shortly%20after%20we%20moved%20in%2C%20costing%20us%20another%20%242%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20those%20hot%20months%2C%20it%20also%20becomes%20prone%20to%20growing%20algae%20and%20I%20find%20myself%20opting%20out%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20pool%20cleaner%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20it%20was%20built%20along%20with%20the%20house%20nearly%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20it's%20showing%20wear%20and%20tear.%20Our%20pool%20cleaner%20told%20me%20that%20relining%20it%20could%20cost%20anywhere%20from%20%2410%2C000%20to%20%2420%2C000%2C%20so%20I%20guess%20we'll%20just%20be%20using%20a%20less-than-photogenic%20pool%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELiving%