6.25%20lakhs%20each%2C%20totalling%20to%20Rs%201.25%20crore.%20And%20another%2032%20odd%20%E2%80%9Ctemporary%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20each%20(a%20modest%20Rs%2040%20lakh).%20This%20is%20essentially%20having%20a%20life-size%203D%20model%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20(they%20also%20have%20lower%20budget%20two-dimension%20life-size%20cutouts)%2C%20props%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20beside%20Modi%20and%20take%20selfies%20with%20their%20phone%20cameras.%20Circulated%20on%20social%20media%2C%20this%20is%20designed%20to%20pep%20up%20the%20popularity%20of%20our%20beloved%20PM.%20These%20props%20also%20have%20texts%20and%20images%20that%20highlight%20some%20flagship%20schemes%2C%20programmes%20or%20achievements%20by%20national%20or%20state%20agencies%2C%20for%20which%20the%20government%20seeks%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20cellspacing%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20cellpadding%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F7090e161-9828-44de-a5f3-069788eb7b9c%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F7090e161-9828-44de-a5f3-069788eb7b9c%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1703911000338000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0uQUWHG7feY-94Zg-hFgNi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fci3.googleusercontent.com%2Fmeips%2FADKq_NaxMTAhZ4n7LiC8DvLNJ_YEx_uqZVa77XDqS8-9YdUsc3nTQagiV_aJAM8v_Wehh1W1-X3fd8uUJ6UE2p1RSdn01-qyUlBLxkdWfplP-kSDDbVd1zF1RfD0W23AVvgsrrm1LM8HNyIy7Ob9MuSDuOEjj78oK8CiZMFyO47AJbb