ress%2019321%20derailed%20near%20Pukhrayan%20in%20Kanpur%2C%20killing%20at%20least%20150%20and%20injuring%20more%20than%20that%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2026%2C%202014%2C%20in%20the%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%20area%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Gorakhdham%20Express%20collided%20with%20a%20halted%20goods%20train%20near%20Khalilabad%20station%2C%20resulting%20in%2025%20fatalities%20and%20leaving%20more%20than%2050%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-on-indian-railways-expenses-ayushman-bharat-graft-diversion-of-pension-scheme-funds%5C%22%3ECAG%20on%20Indian%20Railways%E2%80%99%20Expenses%2C%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Graft%2C%20Diversion%20of%20Pension%20Scheme%20Funds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20blessed%20Railway%20Minister%2C%20the%20brief%20is%20clear.%20Millions%20visit%20railway%20stations%20every%20day.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20take%20political%20advantage%20of%20this%20captive%20crowd%2C%20to%20generate%20optics%20to%20promote%20the%20persona%20of%20PM%20Modi%20and%20his%20%E2%80%9Cachievements%E2%80%9D.%20In%20an%20aeroplane%2C%20the%20passengers%20are%20forced%20to%20listen%20to%20government%20propaganda.%20Full%20marks%20to%20the%20Ministry%20for%20Aviation.%20(Thankfully%2C%20though%2C%20the%20selfie%20booth%20has%20not%20yet%20found%20its%20way%20into%20the%20aisle%20space.)%20Why%20are%20the%20Railways%20lagging%20behind%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriorities%20are%20made%20clear%20to%20the%20minister.%20The%20budget%20for%20improving%20rail%20safety%2C%20or%20to%20provide%20enough%20sleeper%20berths%20and%20seats%20for%20passengers%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ecan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0be%20put%20into%20better%20use%20for%20much%20more%20nationalistic%20purposes%2C%20like%20erecting%20selfie%20booths%20to%20take%20pictures%20with%20Modi.%20I%20do%20not%20recall%20the%20expenditure%20head%20of%20selfie%20booths%20being%20spoken%20of%20in%20Parliament%20in%20the%202023%20Budget%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Railways%2C%20especially%20its%20deteriorating%20safety%20standards%2C%20is%20a%20terror%2C%20though%20it%20is%20the%20lifeline%20of%20our%20nation.%20But%20who%20cares%3F%20The%20minister%E2%80%99s%20boss%20will%20get%20happy%20only%20if%20he%20installs%20enough%20selfie%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20spending%20money%20for%20this%20nonsense%3F%20Yes%2C%20it%20is%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20put%20their%20lives%20at%20risk%20by%20travelling%20on%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Railways%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20goes%20through%20severe%20hardships%20to%20travel%20by%20train%20when%20the%20Railways%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20non-AC%20sleeper%20berths%20to%20favour%20luxurious%20AC%20accommodation%20for%20the%20rich%3F%20Yes%2C%20right%20again%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20government%20is%20without%20doubt%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuit-boot%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eki%20sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20It%20serves%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0the%20rich%2C%20and%20government%20funds%20are%20used%20only%20to%20prop%20up%20an%20insecure%20and%20inadequate%20narcissistic%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Koshy%20is%20a%20consultant%20in%20the%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20engineering%20sector.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22message-text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22block-kit-renderer%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20T