pan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20they%20contend%2C%20what%20we%20dub%20%E2%80%98reality%E2%80%99%20is%20often%20only%20constituted%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20of%20narratives%20which%20owe%20no%20being%20or%20allegiance%20to%20any%20unshakable%20or%20rooted%20truths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20an%20intellectually%20engaging%20take%20on%20the%20often%20frustrating%20substance%20of%20human%20endeavours%2C%20but%20one%20that%20rather%20cleverly%20evades%20from%20a%20secure%20class%20position%20the%20quite%20determinable%20fact%20that%20such%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%2C%20be%20it%20of%20narratives%20or%20identities%2C%20is%20invariably%20linked%20to%20the%20pursuit%20of%20one%20form%20or%20another%20of%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHuman%20agents%20never%20cease%20to%20deploy%20what%20seem%20inconsistent%20narratives%20to%20obtain%20dominance%20over%20definitions%2C%20institutions%2C%20systems%20of%20governance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20when%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20was%20heard%20to%20make%20reference%20to%20his%20social%20identity%20in%20open%20session%20%E2%80%93%20a%20procedure%20frowned%20upon%20upon%20by%20constitutional%20etiquette%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20drawing%20upon%20a%20social%20resource%20that%20he%20felt%20at%20the%20time%20might%20have%20more%20traction%20among%20a%20television%20audience%20than%20his%20identities%20as%20vice-president%20of%20India%20and%20and%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20mere%20idle%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20of%20an%20identity%20that%20but%20one%20cannily%20directed%20to%20a%20political%20purpose.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20of%20course%20few%20other%20nations%20that%20offer%20quite%20the%20same%20mind-boggling%20spread%20of%20identities%20as%20does%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20fact%20makes%20politics%20in%20India%20both%20endlessly%20frustrating%20and%20fascinating%20all%20at%20once.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELately%2C%20given%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20adroitness%20at%20sophistry%20(making%20false%20arguments%20stand%20for%20the%20lurking%20factual%20ones)%2C%20the%20forthcoming%20general%20elections%20are%20generating%20a%20most%20instructive%20skein%20of%20%E2%80%98takes%E2%80%99%20on%20who%20is%20who%20among%20contenders%20for%20state%20power%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20man%20is%20now%20a%20pure%2C%20socially%20undifferentiated%20nationalist%2C%20and%20now%20a%20protagonist%20of%20this%20or%20that%20social%20group%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20not%20excluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20latest%20play%20is%20to%20foreground%20some%20demographic%20categories%20as%20the%20real%20four%20castes%20in%20India%2C%20do%20remember%20that%20he%20also%20gently%20reminds%20us%20now%20and%20again%20how%20he%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20numero%20uno%20of%20independent%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20back-and-forth%20of%20owning%20or%20disowning%20identities%20from%20time%20to%20time%20now%20can%20be%20seen%20to%20shape%20the%20canny%20calculations%20of%20segments%20of%20the%20electorate%20across%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20especially.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20a%20pretty%20ingenuous%20and%20politically%20telling%20sample%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%207%20o%E2%80%99clock%20evening%20bulletin%20of%20the%20electronic%20news%20channel%2C%20News%2024%2C%20in%20its%20popular%20programme%20%E2%80%98Mahol%20Kya%20Hai%20(what%20is%20the%20political%20weather%20like).%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fmimicry-jagdeep-dhankhar-kalyan-banerjee%5C%22%3EWe%20Were%20Created%20in%20Our%20Creator%E2%80%99s%20Image%20%E2%80%93%20Mimicry%20Is%20Our%20Manifest%20Destiny%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anchor%20in%20attendance%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20saffron%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esadri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereinforced%20by%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekalava%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20around%20his%20wrist%20seemed%20to%20have%20a%20clear-enough%20agenda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20anxious%20to%20elicit%20from%20his%20exclusive%20Jat%20audience%20in%20Hapur%2C%20a%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20area%2C%20assent%20to%20the%20proposition%20that%20in%20mimicking%20Dhankhar%2C%20the%20political%20opposition%20had%20insulted%20all%20jats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImportant%20to%20note%20that%20this%20programme%20featured%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20late%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20whom%20Jats%20especially%20credit%20with%20having%20been%20not%20just%20their%20tallest%20leader%20%2C%20but%20of%20all%20agriculturists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStunningly%20came%20a%20retort%20that%20the%20only%20authentic%20Jats%20were%20the%20followers%20of%20that%20great%20departed%20leader%20and%2C%20then%2C%20of%20his%20lineage%20now%20led%20by%20his%20grandson%2C%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%3B%20those%20Jats%20who%20had%20their%20loyalties%20elsewhere%20were%20not%20Jats%20but%20Hindus!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nationalist%20right-wing%20of%20course%20continues%20to%20be%20frustrated%20by%20this%20most%20distressing%20schism%20among%20Indian%20Hindus%3A%20they%20re%20both%20Hindus%20with%20religious%20allegiances%20and%2C%20simultaneously%2C%20proud%20members%20of%20caste%20groups%20which%20they%20uphold%20as%20being%20more%20intimate%20to%20their%20concrete%20and%20grounded%20livelihoods%20than%20their%20rather%20more%20abstruse%20and%20undifferentiated%20religious%20oneness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ruling%20political%20conglomeration%20is%20thus%20constrained%20constantly%20to%20now%20deny%20the%20one%20and%20own%20the%20other%2C%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20never%20quite%20able%20yet%20to%20extinguish%20the%20social%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20denominational%20as%20its%20monochromatic%20ideological%20purpose%20requires.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20dance%20of%20necessity%20of%20course%20is%20distorted%20by%20grave%20and%20in-your-face%20contradictions%20which%20often%20the%20best%20of%20their%20sophistry%20fails%20to%20eschew.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%2C%20for%20example%2C%20asked%20why%20Dhankhar%E2%80%99s%20proud%20social%20allegiance%20did%20not%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20globally%20decorated%20Jat%20women%20wrestlers%20were%20shamefully%20humiliated%20throughout%20their%20prolonged%20protest%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20alleged%20%E2%80%98sexual%20harassment%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20man%20then%20incharge%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%2C%20only%20very%20pathetic%20and%20lame%20answers%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20from%20the%20spokespersons%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F15093117%2Fdownload-e1684123572882.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F15093117%2Fdownload-e1684123572882.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F15093117%2Fdownload-e1684123572882-300x185.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-653024%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22