e%20permanent%20deletion%20of%20personal%20data%20from%20users%20who%20have%20been%20inactive%20for%20three%20consecutive%20years.%20The%20rules%20will%20also%20extend%20to%20ecommerce%20companies%2C%20online%20marketplaces%2C%20and%20gaming%20intermediaries.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20draft%20rules%20propose%20allowing%20healthcare%20professionals%20and%20educational%20institutes%20to%20use%20publicly%20available%20personal%20and%20non-personal%20data%20for%20research%20and%20public%20health%20purposes.%20In%20case%20of%20data%20breaches%2C%20intermediaries%20must%20inform%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Board%20and%20their%20users%20within%2072%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Ffacebook-instagram-and-other-social-media-companies-may-have-to-delete-data-of-these-users%2Farticleshow%2F106358045.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unhappy%20New%20Year%20for%20the%20Gorkha%20Brigade%2C%20Downsizing%20and%20Ultimate%20Phasing%20Out%20Becoming%20a%20Reality%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F25161451%2F27440629405_563f1699dc_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%2011%2C%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Pushpa%20Kamal%20Dahal%20Prachanda%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20Nepali%20citizens%20are%20not%20only%20serving%20the%20Russian%20Army%20but%20also%20reportedly%20serving%20in%20the%20Ukranian%20Army%E2%80%9D.%20Nepal%20has%20urged%20Russia%20to%20stop%20their%20recruitment%20%E2%80%93%20almost%20200%20Nepali%20citizens%20have%20joined%20the%20Russian%20Army%20under%20dubious%20circumstances%20and%20six%20Nepalis%20have%20been%20reportedly%20killed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20to%20investigate%20the%20number%20of%20Nepalis%20fighting%20for%20Ukraine.%20Some%20have%20also%20joined%20the%20French%20Foreign%20Legion%2C%20such%20is%20the%20adverse%20effect%20of%20Nepal%20apparently%20rejecting%20Agniveer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Mukund%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EFour%20Stars%20of%20Destiny%3C%2Fem%3E%20spills%20the%20beans%20over%20the%20ownership%20of%20Agniveer%20scheme.%20As%20we%20have%20known%2C%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frss-ajit-doval-coerced-agniveer-scheme-on-the-army-rahul-gandhi-in-lok-sabha%2Farticleshow%2F97693965.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethrust%20on%20the%20three%20services%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(PMO)%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20(NSA)%20Ajit%20Doval%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20stated%20in%20parliament.%20Originally%20designed%20by%20late%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%2C%20it%20was%20to%20be%20a%20pilot%20project%20for%205%2C000%20Army%20personnel%20but%20the%20transformative%20reform%20took%20all%20three%20services%20by%20surprise%20says%20Naravane.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%20at%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Chanakya%20Dialogue%20a%20former%20Navy%20chief%20said%20that%20former%20CNS%20Admiral%20Karamvir%20Singh%20had%20rejected%2C%20in%20writing%2C%20the%20draft%20Agniveer%20scheme.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20manipulation%20of%20incumbent%20service%20chiefs%20in%20praising%20the%20Agniveer%20project%20is%20astounding.%20What%20no%20government%20or%20military%20official%20has%20revealed%20is%20the%20stalemate%20over%20recruitment%20of%20Nepali%20Gorkha%20Agniveers%20since%20June%202022%20and%20the%20Covid%20embargo%20period.%20Had%20General%20Rawat%2C%20a%20second%20generation%20Gorkha%20officer%20been%20alive%2C%20Agniveer%20in%20its%20current%20avatar%20would%20not%20have%20materialised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spent%20the%20last%20month%20in%20Pokhara%2C%20Nepal%2C%20the%20heartland%20of%20Nepal%20Domiciled%20Gorkhas%20(NDG)%20recruitment%2C%20interacting%20with%20ex-servicemen%20and%20other%20stakeholders.%20Not%20a%20single%20NDG%20has%20been%20recruited%20or%20become%20an%20Agniveer%20for%20nearly%20four%20years.%20Nepal%C2%A0%20has%C2%A0%20not%20communicated%20any%20reason%20for%20not%20subscribing%20to%20the%20Agniveer%20project.%20The%20Tripartite%20Treaty%20of%201947%20governed%20Gorkha%20recruitment%20from%20Nepal%20by%20the%20British%20and%20Indian%20Armies.%20In%20June%202022%2C%20India%20announced%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20without%20consulting%20Nepal.%20Gorkhas%20are%20recognised%20as%20great%20warriors%20around%20the%20world%20and%20were%20key%20to%20the%20British%20empire%20that%20extended%20from%20Honduras%20to%20Hong%20Kong.%20In%202014%2C%20prime%20minister%20Modi%20praised%20the%20Gorkhas%20for%20shedding%20their%20blood%20for%20protecting%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20India.%20For%20India%2C%20Gorkhas%20joining%20Indian%20Army%20is%20much%20more%20that%20%E2%80%98recruitment%E2%80%99.%20It%20represents%20the%20strategic%20bonding%20between%20India%20and%20Nepal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-china-army-nepali-gorkhas-worry%5C%22%3EWhy%20India%20Should%20Be%20Worried%20About%20Chinese%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Plans%20to%20Recruit%20Nepali%20Gorkhas%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENepal%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20led%20government%20in%202022%20passed%20on%20the%20decision%20on%20Agniveer%20to%20the%20new%20Maoist-led%20government%20which%20said%20it%20was%20seeking%20political%20consensus%20%E2%80%93%20diplomatic%20euphemism%20for%20rejecting%20Agniveer.%C2%A0%20In%20Nepal%2C%20public%20view%20on%20the%20scheme%20is%20divided.%C2%A0%20Most%20find%20it%20to%20be%20deeply%20flawed%20but%20their%20bottom%20line%20is%20firmly%20centered%20on%20pensionary%20benefits.%20The%20generous%20One%20Rank%2C%20One%20Pension%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(OROP)%20has%20transformed%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20of%20the%20ex-servicemen.%20The%20minority%20view%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Csomething%20(Agniveer)%20is%20better%20than%20nothing%E2%80%9D%20highlights%20the%20need%20of%20job-seekers%20even%20if%20it%20for%20four%20years%20sans%20pension.%20But%20politics%20has%20trumped%20strategic%20and%20financial%20factors.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20elections%2C%20Communist%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20CPN%20UML%2C%20CPN%20Maoist%20and%20CPN%20Socialist%20%E2%80%93%20captured%2068%25%20of%20the%20vote.%20The%20Maoists%E2%80%99%2040-point%20demand%20in%201990%20prior%20to%20the%20civil%20war%20demanded%20abrogation%20of%20foreign%20recruitment%20especially%20in%20Indian%20Army.%20No%20government%20in%20the%20coalition%20era%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20that%20has%20become%20inevitable%20under%20the%20new%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20can%20oppose%20Communist%20thinking%2C%20especially%20on%20Agniveer.%20The%20hope%20that%20under%20the%20power-sharing%20agreement%2C%20after%20one%20year%2C%20the%20Nepali%20Congress-led%20coalition%20will%20accept%20Agniveer%20is%20unrealistic.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20Nepal%20Army%20Chief%20Lt.%20General%20Prabhu%20Sharma%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20honorary%20General%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20said%20that%20he%20is%20not%20against%20recruitment%20in%20Indian%20Army%20but%20he%20is%20against%20recruitment%20as%20Agniveer.%20In%201974%2C%20an%20unstrategic%20Indian%20project%20to%20terminate%20Gorkha%20recruitment%20was%20aborted%3B%C2%A0%20then%20Army%20chief%2C%20General%20Gopal%20Bewoor%20from%2011%20Gorkha%20Rifles%20persuaded%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20dump%20the%20lunatic%20scheme.%20Today%20we%20have%20a%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%2C%C2%A0%20General%20Anil%20Chauhan%2C%20from%20same%20the%20Gorkha%20regiment%20but%20the%20manner%20of%20his%20deep%20selection%20has%20compromised%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%2C%20for%20now%2C%20is%20determined%20not%20to%20budge%20from%20Agniveer%20.%20Two%20reasons%20are%20offered%20%E2%80%93%20first%2C%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20end%20Gorkha%20recruitment%20as%20there%20is%20sufficient%20male%20recruitable%20population%20(MRP)%20in%20India.%20The%20more%20compelling%20reason%20is%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20dismantling%20colonial%20legacy%20of%20recruitment%20of%20foreign%20soldiers.%20The%20real%20reason%20though%20is%20financial%20%E2%80%93%20salary%20and%20pension%20costs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgniveer%20is%20designed%20to%20reduce%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20Army%20and%20cut%20pensions.%20The%20latter%20alone%20in%202021-22%20accounted%20for%20Rs%201.21%20lakh%20crore%20which%20was%20more%20than%20allotment%20for%20modernisation.%20Av%20(Agniveer)%20is%20the%20rank%20prefix%20of%20a%20soldier%20and%20is%20the%20lowest%20rank%20in%20PBOR%20(Personnel%20Below%20Officer%20Rank).%20This%20is%20a%20new%20rank%20and%20tenable%20by%20Agniveers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENepal%20is%20conveying%20to%20India%20that%20Agniveer%20is%20breach%20of%20Tripartite%20Agreement%20of%201947%20and%20consensus%20is%20required%20between%20original%20signatories%20to%20change%20terms%20of%20engagement%3B%20and%20in%20order%20to%20accept%20Agniveer%2C%20the%20ruling%20government%20is%20seeking%20political%20consensus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20future%20of%20the%20Gorkha%20Brigade%20and%20its%2038%20battalions%20is%20bleak%20given%20the%20inflexible%20positions%20of%20both%20countries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20after%20returning%20from%20Nepal%2C%20following%20his%20appointment%20as%20honorary%20General%20of%20Nepal%20Army%2C%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20General%20Manoj%20Pandey%20said%20this%20on%20Gorkha%20recruitment%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20decide%20soon%20their%20vacancies%20will%20be%20given%20to%20others%E2%80%9D.%20As%20there%20has%20been%20no%20recruitment%20for%20four%20years%2C%20a%20shortfall%20in%20Gorkha%20regiment%20is%20being%20made%20up%20by%20Kumaonis%2C%20Garhwalis%20and%20now%20Nagas%20while%20other%20tribes%20are%20being%20considered.%20General%20Pande%20is%20also%20mulling%20over%20reducing%20Gorkha%20battalions.%20Indian%20Domiciled%20Gorkhas%20who%20constitute%2040%25%20of%20recruitment%20are%20not%20a%20match%20for%20NDGs.%20In%202017%2C%206%2F1%20Gorkha%20Rifles%20was%20raised%20comprising%20100%25%20IDGs.%20It%20has%20become%20difficult%20now%20to%20preserve%206%2F1%20GR%E2%80%99s%20IDG%20sanctity%20and%20content%20as%20few%20IDGs%20meet%20the%20qualitative%20requirements%20(QRs)%20even%20after%20lowering%20standards%20and%20fewer%20are%20available.%20So%20the%20plan%20to%20fill%20up%20NDG%20shortfall%20with%20IDGs%20is%20a%20non-starter.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20his%20visit%20to%20India%20in%20June%2C%20prime%20minister%20Dahal%20did%20not%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20Agniveer.%20Nepali%20foreign%20minister%20Narayan%20Saud%20told%20the%20BBC%20in%20August%20that%20any%20alteration%20of%20Tripartite%20Treaty%20between%20Nepal%2C%20India%20and%20UK%20must%20be%20based%20on%20consensus.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EStrangely%2C%20neither%20Nepal%20nor%20India%20has%20cared%20to%20call%20for%20talks%20on%20Agniveer.%20Meanwhile%2C%20recruitment%20is%20restricted%20to%20IDGs%20and%20tradesmen.%20The%20Gorkha%20Training%20Centres%20are%20training%20them%20and%20Agniveers%20of%20Indian%20regiments.%C2%A0%20The%20Colonel%20of%20Gorkha%20Brigade%20Lt.%20General%20Ajai%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20General%20Officer%20Commanding%20(GOC)%20in%20C%20Southern%20Command%20and%20has%20served%20in%20Nepal%2025%20years%20ago%20as%20a%20Pension%20Paying%20Officer%2C%20is%20visiting%20Nepal%20as%20President%20of%20the%20Gorkha%20Brigade%20next%20month%20and%20will%20meet%20cabinet%20ministers%20and%20government%20officials%20besides%20ex-servicemen%20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20stunning%20irony%20that%20just%20when%20India%20is%20celebrating%20the%20biopic%20Sam%20Bahadur%20on%20Field%20Marshal%20Manekshaw%2C%20who%20became%20a%20household%20name%20in%20India%20and%20Nepal%20owing%20to%20his%20bonding%20with%20Gorkhas%2C%20their%20downsizing%20and%20ultimate%20phasing%20out%20is%20becoming%20a%20reality.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%202030%20there%20will%20be%20no%20pure%20Gorkha%20battalions%20and%20about%20half%20present%20number%3B%20and%20by%202037%2C%20none%20at%20all.%20This%20government%20will%20be%20credited%20with%20ending%20foreign%20recruitment%20but%20snapping%20a%20strategic%20connection%20with%20the%20most%20crucially%20located%20neighbour%20while%C2%A0%20opening%20the%20door%20to%20Nepali%20Gorkhas%20in%20PLA%20in%20the%20not%20too%20distant%20future.%20India-Nepal%20relations%20will%20never%20be%20the%20same%20again.%20Not%20a%20happy%20new%20year%20for%20the%20Gorkha%20Brigade!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAshok%20K.%20Mehta%2C%20a%20major%20general%2C%20is%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Defence%20Planning%20Staff%20now%20the%20Integrated%20Defence%20Staff.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703777426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F25161451%2F27440629405_563f1699dc_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Funhappy-new-year-for-the-gorkha-brigade-downsizing-and-ultimate-phasing-out-becoming-a-reality%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20government%20will%20be%20credited%20with%20ending%20foreign%20recruitment%20but%20also%20of%20snapping%20a%20strategic%20connection%20with%20a%20crucially%20located%20neighbour%20while%C2%A0opening%20the%20door%20to%20Nepali%20Gorkhas%20in%20PLA%20in%20the%20not%20too%20distant%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A102%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%